 creeks and streams,\nurban areas, highways, streets and underpasses.\n\n* Some locations that will experience flash flooding include...\nNorwood and Placerville, including areas along Highway 145.","ends":"2026-07-21T19:30:00-06:00","severity":"Severe","areaDesc":"Montrose, CO; San Miguel, CO","id":"urn:oid:2.49.0.1.840.0.44e535cb74b4e563bb4fc6013222810e4455d2aa.001.1","url":"https://api.weather.gov/alerts/urn:oid:2.49.0.1.840.0.44e535cb74b4e563bb4fc6013222810e4455d2aa.001.1"}],"afd":{"office":"GJT","issued":"2026-07-21T23:52:00+00:00","snippet":"000 FXUS65 KGJT 212352 AFDGJT Area Forecast Discussion National Weather Service Grand Junction CO 552 PM MDT Tue Jul 21 2026 .KEY MESSAGES... - Showers and storms will continue this week each afternoon and evening, with coverage becoming more widespread by Tuesday and Wednesday. - Primary threats include heavy rainfall, lightning, and outflow winds up to 30-40 mph. Small hail cannot be ruled out i","url":"https://forecast.weather.gov/product.php?site=GJT&issuedby=GJT&product=AFD&format=CI"},"hwo":null,"coagmet":{"station_id":"nwd01","station_name":"Norwood","distance_km":2.3,"soil_temp_5cm_f":73.58,"soil_temp_15cm_f":71.22,"soil_moisture_5cm":null,"soil_moisture_15cm":null,"precip_in":null,"eto_in":null,"vapor_pressure":null,"solar_radiation":11.47,"wind_speed_mph":7.01,"air_temp_f":69.22,"relative_humidity":0.574,"url":"https://coagmet.colostate.edu/station/nwd01"},"aviation":{"icao":"KTEX","distance_km":0,"raw_metar":"METAR KTEX 220055Z AUTO 00000KT 10SM -RA SCT075 OVC090 17/11 A3047 RMK AO2","temp_f":63,"wind_dir":0,"wind_kt":0,"gust_kt":null,"visibility":"10+","cover":"OVC","flight_category":"VFR","altimeter":1031.9,"observed":1784681700,"raw_taf":"TAF KTEX 212340Z 2200/2224 18006KT P6SM VCTS SCT060CB BKN100 TEMPO 2200/2204 VRB25G45KT -TSRA BKN060CB FM220400 14007KT P6SM SCT080 BKN100 PROB30 2206/2210 4SM -TSRA BKN060CB OVC080 FM221800 VRB05KT P6SM -TSRA SCT045CB BKN090","url":"https://aviationweather.gov/data/metar/?i